5 Irvine Street, Bayswater represents a unique opportunity for the emerging entrepreneur.  This tidy, part leased office/warehouse facility provides the perfect home for a developing business with attractive holding income from a longstanding tenant.    

Located within proximity to Tonkin Highway, Collier Road and Beechboro Road South, the property features two freestanding office/warehouses on a fully fenced allotment.  The current owner operates a small business from the rear building while the street front building is leased on an extended 3-year term to a well-regarded local business.

Key Features:
-	Front Warehouse: 250sqm*
-	Front Office: 40sqm* + mezzanine storage
-	Rear Office/Warehouse: 140sqm*
-	Rear yard area
-	Fully fenced site

Lease Summary:
-	Rental Income: $30,000 pa + Outgoings + GST
-	Term: 3 years (expiring 13th July 2019)
-	Option: 2 Years (commencing 14th July 2019)

*Approximate

For further information, please do not hesitate to call the exclusive selling agents.

CBRE are pleased to present this 188sqm* affordable warehouse with small office located centrally within the strategic and well established Bayswater industrial precinct. 

Features include kitchenette, 2 x toilets, ample power points throughout, 2 x car bays, mezzanine storage area, small internal workshop/tool store and good natural lighting.

Recent upgrade works include:

- Motorised roller door
- Upgraded roof insulation
- LED high bay lights
- Freshly painted throughout

*approx

This is a brand new building with completion due April-May 2021, property features as follows:

- 2,310 sqm total land area
- 1,645 sqm total floor area
- 117 sqm ground floor office
- 117 sqm first floor office
- 52 sqm mezzanine storage area with concrete slab
- 1,359 sqm high truss warehouse
- Two 5m x 5m electric heavy duty roller shutters to warehouse
- Approx 398 sqm separate yard / lock up area with 6m x 6m electric roller shutter
- 8 - 8.5m high truss to warehouse
- Ground floor shower x2
- Ducted air conditioning to office areas & lunchroom
- Carpet tiles to office areas
- NBN connection
- Stone benchtops to kitchen and toilet vanities
- Ultracore G2 cladding to office facade
- 19 marked car bays includes allowance for FFL Storage to become Office with sufficient bays
- Landscaping
- 1800mm black Garrison secure fencing with automatic sliding gate
